data.text:
Description

Funeral program for Mildred M. Doisedo, born October 12, 1914 and died September 28, 2008. The funeral was held October 4, 2008 at Second Baptist Church. The funeral arrangements were made through Lewis Funeral Home and she was buried in Meadowlawn Memorial Park in San Antonio, Texas.

Physical Description

1 pamphlet : col. ill. ; 22 x 28 cm., folded to 22 x 14 cm.
